import{_ as e,o,c as t,b as r}from"./app-a6eacc5a.js";const s={},d=r('<h1 id="embedded-software" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#embedded-software" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Embedded Software</h1><p><code>Embedded</code> software refers to software that is designed and developed specifically for use in embedded systems, which are computer systems that are <code>integrated</code> into other devices or machines. Embedded systems are typically used in <em>a wide range of</em> applications, including <code>automotive</code>, <code>aerospace</code>, medical, industrial, and consumer electronics.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 嵌入式软件是指专门为在嵌入式系统中使用而设计和开发的软件，嵌入式系统是集成到其他设备或机器中的计算机系统。嵌入式系统通常用于广泛的应用领域，包括汽车、航空、医疗、工业和消费电子等。</p><p><strong>phrase:</strong><br> a wide range of -&gt; 广泛的范围：涵盖很多种类或数量的事物。</p><p><strong>words:</strong><br> embedded<br><code>英 [ɪmˈbedɪd]美 [ɪmˈbedɪd]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 嵌入（或插入、埋入）……之中的；（感情、态度等）深切的；被士兵保护的<br> v. 使插入，使嵌入；（态度、感情等）植根于，使融入；嵌入，插入（图片、声音、软件等）（embed 的过去式和过去分词）</p></blockquote><p>integrate ( integrating, integrated, integrates )<br><code>英 [ˈɪntɪɡreɪt]美 [ˈɪntɪɡreɪt]</code></p><blockquote><p>v. （使）合并，成为一体；（使）加入，融入群体；（使）取消种族隔离；求……的积分；表示（面积、温度等）的总和，表示……的平均值<br> adj. 整合的</p></blockquote><p>automotive<br><code>英 [ˌɔːtəˈməʊtɪv]美 [ˌɔːtəˈmoʊtɪv]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 汽车的；自动的</p></blockquote><p>aerospace<br><code>英 [ˈeərəʊspeɪs]美 [ˈeroʊspeɪs]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 航空航天工业，航空航天技术；航空与航天空间<br> adj. 航空和航天（工业）的，宇航的</p></blockquote></details><p>Embedded software is different from traditional desktop or server software in several ways. First, it must be small enough to <code>fit</code> within the limited memory and processing power of an embedded system. Second, it must be highly reliable and <code>efficient</code>, as errors or <code>crashes</code> can have serious consequences in an embedded system. Third, it often requires <code>specialized</code> knowledge and skills to develop and maintain, as the hardware and software must work together <code>seamlessly</code>.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong></p><p>嵌入式软件在几个方面不同于传统的桌面或服务器软件。首先，它必须足够小，以适应嵌入式系统的有限内存和处理能力。其次，它必须高度可靠和高效，因为错误或崩溃在嵌入式系统中可能会产生严重的后果。第三，开发和维护通常需要专门的知识和技能，因为硬件和软件必须无缝地协同工作。</p><p><strong>words:</strong><br> fit<br><code>英: [fɪt] 美: [fɪt]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 健壮的；健康的；（质量、素质或技能）适合的<br> n. （癫痫等的）突发；昏厥；痉挛；一阵（忍不住的咳嗽、笑）<br> v. 合身；（大小、式样、数量适合）可容纳；试穿（衣服）；安置<br> adv. 适合地；适时地</p></blockquote><p>efficient<br><code>英 [ɪˈfɪʃ(ə)nt]美 [ɪˈfɪʃ(ə)nt]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 生效的，效率高的；（人）有能力的，能胜任的</p></blockquote><p>crash ( crashing, crashed, crashes )<br><code>英: [kræʃ] 美: [kræʃ]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 崩溃；坠毁；撞击；速成<br> v. 撞；破产；打碎；粉碎<br> adj. 紧急的<br> adv. 砰地一声</p></blockquote><p>specialized<br><code>英 [ˈspeʃəlaɪzd]美 [ˈspeʃəlaɪzd]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 专业的，专门的<br> v. 专门研究（或从事），专攻；专营；（生）使（器官）专化，使特化（specialize 的过去式和过去分词）</p></blockquote><p>seamlessly<br><code>英 [ˈsiːmləsli]美 [ˈsiːmləsli]</code></p><blockquote><p>adv. 无缝地</p></blockquote></details><p>Some common types of embedded software include operating systems, device drivers, <code>firmware</code>, and application programs.<br> Operating systems are the core components of an embedded system, providing a platform for running applications and managing resources such as memory and input/output devices.<br> Device drivers allow embedded systems to communicate with <code>external</code> devices such as sensors, <code>actuators</code>, and displays.<br> Firmware is the low-level software that runs on the <code>microcontroller</code> or other processor in an embedded system, controlling the behavior of the system&#39;s hardware.<br> Application programs are user-facing software that provides <code>specific</code> functionality to end users.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 一些常见类型的嵌入式软件包括操作系统、设备驱动程序、固件和应用程序。<br> 操作系统是嵌入式系统的核心竞争力，为运行应用程序和管理资源(如内存和输入/输出设备)提供平台。 设备驱动程序允许嵌入式系统与外部设备(如传感器、执行器和显示器)通信。<br> 固件是运行在嵌入式系统的微控制器或其他处理器上的底层软件，控制系统硬件的行为。<br> 应用程序是面向用户的软件，向最终用户提供特定功能。</p><p><strong>words:</strong><br> firmware<br><code>英 [ˈfɜːmweə(r)]美 [ˈfɜːrmwer]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 固件；韧件</p></blockquote><p>external<br><code>英 [ɪkˈstɜːn(ə)l]美 [ɪkˈstɜːrn(ə)l]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 外部的，外面的；对外的，与外国有关的；外来的，外聘的；（药品等类似物质）外用的<br> n. 外表，外部特征</p></blockquote><p>actuator<br><code>英 [ˈæktʃʊeɪtə(r)]美 [ˈæktʃueɪtər]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. [自] 执行机构；激励者；促动器；致动器</p></blockquote><p>microcontroller<br><code>英 [maɪkrəʊkɒntˈrəʊlə(r)]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. [自] 微控制器</p></blockquote><p>specific<br><code>英: [spə&#39;sɪfɪk] 美: [spəˈsɪfɪk]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 特性；细节；特效药；特殊用途的事物<br> adj. 明确的；具体的；特定的；特有的</p></blockquote></details>',7),a=[d];function c(n,i){return o(),t("div",null,a)}const l=e(s,[["render",c],["__file","14-embedded-software.html.vue"]]);export{l as default};
